    Agent --> Runtime
    Runtime --> Task

    %% =====================================================
    %% Workflow Logic
    %% =====================================================

    subgraph Logic["Workflow Control Flow"]

        Start["Start"]

        Step1["Task"]

        Decision{"Condition"}

        Parallel["Parallel Tasks"]

        Wait["Wait / Delay"]

        Retry["Retry"]

        Step2["Next Task"]

        Complete["Complete"]

        Failed["Failed"]

        Start --> Step1
        Step1 --> Decision

        Decision -->|True| Parallel
        Decision -->|False| Wait

        Parallel --> Step2
        Wait --> Retry

        Retry --> Step2

        Step2 --> Complete

    end

    Task --> Start

