    %% =====================================================

    subgraph State["Workflow State"]

        Status["Execution Status"]
        Variables["Workflow Variables"]
        Checkpoints["Checkpoints"]
        History["Execution History"]

    end

    Planner --> Status
    Step1 --> Variables
    Step2 --> Variables
    Parallel --> Checkpoints
    Complete --> History
    Failed --> History

